You can't get a divorce now that Ryuzaki's been arrested.

1011
01:34:36,908 --> 01:34:39,301
Not because I love Ryuzaki.

1012
01:34:40,669 --> 01:34:50,636
I was going to make you my wife this time, no matter what I had to do, no matter how long it took.

1013
01:34:52,536 --> 01:34:54,156
You can't.

1014
01:34:55,599 --> 01:35:04,055
Seeing my mother when the house was raided made it impossible for me to abandon the Ryuzaki family.

1015
01:35:08,895 --> 01:35:11,229
You should have left him earlier.

1016
01:35:16,093 --> 01:35:18,053
What are you going to do now?

1017
01:35:22,969 --> 01:35:27,489
I'm going to stay with the Ryuzaki family.

1018
01:35:27,959 --> 01:35:32,205
So you won't think of me?

1019
01:35:33,819 --> 01:35:36,986
I won't let you go.

1020
01:36:12,224 --> 01:36:13,524
Good morning.

1021
01:36:14,219 --> 01:36:16,206
Your wife left on an urgent errand.

1022
01:36:18,091 --> 01:36:20,045
She just left.

1023
01:36:44,601 --> 01:36:45,561
I need a car right away.

1024
01:36:45,861 --> 01:36:47,855
Your wife gave me this.

1025
01:36:51,057 --> 01:36:55,404
I am so sorry.
Please forgive my selfishness.

1026
01:36:56,407 --> 01:37:00,113
I said I would stay in Ryuzaki for my mother's sake.

1027
01:37:00,275 --> 01:37:03,408
I'm sure you must feel very sorry for her.

1028
01:37:05,373 --> 01:37:08,006
But that is not why I am leaving you.

1029
01:37:09,465 --> 01:37:21,889
The more I love you, the more a heavy sense of guilt about Natsui and Chikako spreads in my heart.

1030
01:37:23,114 --> 01:37:25,888
Please forget about Ayako.

1031
01:37:27,015 --> 01:37:30,849
I will not see you again. I will bear it and say goodbye.

1032
01:37:45,559 --> 01:37:45,993
Hello?

1033
01:37:46,228 --> 01:37:48,195
Your car is ready.

1034
01:37:50,803 --> 01:37:51,769
I don't need the car anymore.

1035
01:38:37,199 --> 01:38:38,287
Sado?

1036
01:38:39,382 --> 01:38:41,322
I'd like to work for the Bureau of Communications.

1037
01:38:44,338 --> 01:38:46,044
You don't have to go there.

1038
01:38:46,646 --> 01:38:47,952
It's country side.

1039
01:38:49,365 --> 01:38:51,205
I'd like to work there.

1040
01:38:51,729 --> 01:38:53,169
For how long?

1041
01:38:53,442 --> 01:38:54,716
Natsui is here.

1042
01:38:54,906 --> 01:38:55,839
I'll be there soon.

1043
01:38:56,057 --> 01:38:58,284
Six months or a year?

1044
01:38:58,436 --> 01:39:00,410
Until retirement.

1045
01:39:01,200 --> 01:39:02,160
What's the hell?

1046
01:39:03,270 --> 01:39:06,990
I'm so glad you came.
I was afraid you wouldn't come even if I asked you to.

1047
01:39:07,502 --> 01:39:10,422
I have no face to show to Kuse or Ayako

1048
01:39:10,864 --> 01:39:13,270
No, that's what we're saying.

1049
01:39:15,618 --> 01:39:18,591
Please forgive Ayako's mistake.

1050
01:39:20,889 --> 01:39:24,363
She's already been punished a lot for that kind of thing.

1051
01:39:26,566 --> 01:39:31,626
Ayako has a childish, childish old-fashioned streak in her.

1052
01:39:34,934 --> 01:39:38,121
She thought that you and Chikako would be happy together.

1053
01:39:39,176 --> 01:39:43,069
I should have been more pleased with Ayako and Kuse.

1054
01:39:43,316 --> 01:39:48,676
That's impossible.
I don't need that bullshit blessing.

1055
01:39:50,808 --> 01:39:53,688
You had no choice until now.

1056
01:40:04,020 --> 01:40:06,933
Ryuzaki has been arrested.

1057
01:40:09,812 --> 01:40:11,712
Please make Ayako happy.

1058
01:40:14,348 --> 01:40:15,248
Natsui.

1059
01:40:17,632 --> 01:40:20,212
I may be transferred to Sado in the near future.

1060
01:40:21,855 --> 01:40:23,068
I've separated from my wife.

1061
01:40:27,568 --> 01:40:32,675
I told her I was going to live on Sado Island for the rest of my life, and she said she didn't want to be a part of that kind of island life.

1062
01:40:35,984 --> 01:40:38,717
I doubt we'll ever see Ayako again either.

1063
01:40:40,142 --> 01:40:42,176
At least not while we're young.

1064
01:40:42,855 --> 01:40:44,255
Why would you do that?

1065
01:40:46,323 --> 01:40:49,110
I don't know.

1066
01:40:53,063 --> 01:40:56,097
Maybe it's because I love her

1067
01:40:58,293 --> 01:41:00,559
Maybe it's because she loves me.

1068
01:41:02,436 --> 01:41:04,116
Humans are weird

1069
01:41:06,794 --> 01:41:13,354
Kuse
When I learned about Ryuzaki and Chikako, I fell in love with Chikako all over again.

1070
01:41:15,665 --> 01:41:20,738
Do you laugh?
A man who started loving his wife with such a pathetic love...

1071
01:41:22,958 --> 01:41:24,372
I am sure you will be happy!

1072
01:41:25,444 --> 01:41:28,558
You must do a great job for Chikak!

1073
01:41:29,815 --> 01:41:32,128
I'll at least pay attention to the magazines when I'm outside.

1074
01:41:33,547 --> 01:41:34,933
I will do it.

1075
01:41:36,400 --> 01:41:37,206
I will do it.

1076
01:42:14,549 --> 01:42:15,202
Chikako?

1077
01:42:18,528 --> 01:42:19,602
Welcome back.

1078
01:42:22,168 --> 01:42:23,341
I'm sorry.

1079
01:42:25,598 --> 01:42:28,331
I'm sorry.
I'm bad wife.

1080
01:42:31,825 --> 01:42:37,685
I came back here on my own. Can you leave me here?

1081
01:42:44,730 --> 01:42:45,903
I'm sorry.

1082
01:42:46,810 --> 01:42:48,396
I'm not going anywhere.

1083
01:42:53,121 --> 01:42:56,361
Good.
I won't let you go.

1084
01:42:58,403 --> 01:42:59,810
I won't let you go.

1085
01:44:01,533 --> 01:44:07,259
Two months have passed since we parted.
I felt as if I were walking in a dream

1086
01:44:08,649 --> 01:44:11,909
Our mother passed away not long after that.

1087
01:44:13,856 --> 01:44:23,181
Shigetaka's mismanagement has destroyed my mother's zest for life, who had been defending the Ryuzaki family's pride.

1088
01:44:24,620 --> 01:44:31,736
It is thanks to my mother's efforts that Shigetaka and I have decided to divorce.

1089
01:44:32,564 --> 01:44:39,151
Now that I am finally a free woman, I am busy getting my affairs in order.

1090
01:44:41,289 --> 01:44:52,193
I made the decision to come to your side after seeing what happened to Natsui and Chikako.

1091
01:44:53,706 --> 01:44:56,626
I really feel lighter in body and mind.

1092
01:44:58,369 --> 01:45:07,419
Please consider the day I leave for Sado as a new beginning with you, with whom I will no longer be parting.

1093
01:45:17,690 --> 01:45:24,286
THE END

